# Backend testing

- Prefer service-level tests with mocks for subprocess, nginx, and certbot.
- Add FastAPI TestClient tests for new API routes and permission checks.
- Use shared fixtures from `backend/tests/conftest.py` (`temp_settings`, `client`, `auth_session`, `viewer_session`).
- Name tests `test_<behavior>_<expected_outcome>`.
- Never invoke real system binaries (`nginx`, `certbot`, `systemctl`) in unit tests.
